com.nestedbird.util

Class QueryBlockQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestedbird.util.QueryBlockQuery

  • public class QueryBlockQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    The container for a specific query for QueryBlock. The result of whether or not a QueryBlock succeeds is passed into QueryBlockQuery, which does the processing of the result. QueryBlockQuery has a fail and done event, for failures and successes respectively.
